The '''''Steady Lady''''' was a sleek, 500-meter-long fast-haul [[Bulk cruiser/Legends|bulk cruiser]] that could carry 1000 passengers. It was above [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] in [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]] and helped the [[Coruscant Planetary Defense Force]] evacuate refugees from the ''[[Sweet Surprise]]''.

